node.text: In this episode of #FWCooks, @la_yoselin of @todoverde showcases crispy edges and tender interior of versatile jackfruit in a deliciously savory plant-based taco that tastes like carnitas. Seasoned with cumin, chile flakes, and salt and served with a tart, creamy avocado salsa these tacos are a satisfying vegetarian meal.  Tap the link in our bio for the recipe!

node.text: In this episode of #FWCooks, @la_yoselin of @todoverde showcases crispy edges and tender interior of versatile jackfruit in a deliciously savory plant-based taco that tastes like carnitas. Seasoned with cumin, chile flakes, and salt and served with a tart, creamy avocado salsa these tacos are a satisfying vegetarian meal.  Tap the link in our bio for the recipe!

node.text: This scoopable Smoked Salmon Dip recipe features fresh dill, chives, and briny pops of capers that keep it light and fresh. Mayo, sour cream and cream cheese make it smooth and deeply flavorful. Tap the link in our bio for the recipe! 🍽️: @jazzy_the_princess 📸: @jencausey

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Food & Wine on July 26, 2021. May be an image of food and text that says '8 NEW WAYS TO MAKE A PB&J'.

node.text:
We've rounded up 8 new ways to help celebrate and update the American classic PB&J. With these newcomers to the nut butter and jam game, these updated combinations are sure to excite both PB&J loyalists and change-seekers alike. Tap the link in our bio to put a modern spin on the iconic sandwich dynamic duo! 
📸: @caitbensel

node.text:
The well-browned, sugary crisp exterior of this Philly Fluff Cake recipe contrasts to the moist, and tender interior. With rich swirls of bittersweet chocolate and cream cheese, the cake has a gentle sweetness and tang. Tap the link in our bio for the recipe! 
🎂: @annatheo 📸: @jencausey

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Food & Wine on July 25, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text:
This Cherry-Vanilla Clafoutis recipe from F&W Culinary Director at Large @justinchapple gets some unexpected smokiness from being baked on the grill. Whole-wheat flour provides a nutty note to this simple French dessert. Tap the link in our bio for the recipe! 
📸: @protazio

node.text:
Pasta and kale cook on the stovetop as red onion, fresh oregano, and garlic perfume this Sheet Pan Baked Chicken, Feta, Tomatoes, and Kale with Pasta recipe. Serve hot, room temperature, or as a chilled pasta salad. Tap the link in our bio for the recipe! 
🍽️: @karen_rankin67 📸: @jencausey

Pick up a copy of our August issue, on newsstands now! On this month's cover: Summer Fruit Cobbler with Vanilla-Mascarpone Biscuits. Any mixture of fresh summer berries and stone fruits will cook down into a sweet-tart, jammy filling. We've tested and tasted every imaginable combination and they are all guaranteed delicious.
